text: Damian Driscoll (born 12 May 1972) is a former professional rugby league footballer who played as a for the Western Suburbs Magpies, Gold Coast Chargers, Manly-Warringah Sea Eagles, Northern Eagles and Salford City Reds in the 1990s and 2000s. ==References== Category:1972 births Category:Western Suburbs Magpies players Category:Gold Coast Chargers players Category:Manly Warringah Sea Eagles players Category:Northern Eagles players Category:Salford Red Devils players Category:Living people Category:Rugby league props
